question: Please give me all family suites and single rooms which cost 150 per night.
sql_query1:
SELECT Accommodations.RoomNumber 
FROM Accommodations
WHERE (Accommodations.TypeOfAccomodation = "Family Suite" OR Accommodations.TypeOfAccomodation = "Single Room") AND Accommodations.PricePerNight = 150.0
sql_query2:
SELECT Accommodations.RoomNumber 
FROM Accommodations
WHERE Accommodations.TypeOfAccomodation = "Family Suite" OR Accommodations.TypeOfAccomodation = "Single Room" AND Accommodations.PricePerNight = 150.0
interpretation1: List all the rooms that cost 150 per night and are either a family suite or single room.
interpretation2: Show all the family suites listed, also show the single rooms which cost 150 per night.
